### Welcome to My GitHub Page
I am currently a freshman at Yale studying Computer Science, expecting to graduate in May 2019 either finishing with Master's and Bachelor's Degree in CS or a Bachelor's Degree in Electrical Engineering and Computer Science. I'm from Taipei, Taiwan, but moved to New Haven, Connecticut in 2015 for college education. I am an enthusiastic and active software developer, worked on several projects, and participating in coder events both in Taipei and at Yale.

####For more information about me, please redirect to [this website](http://kenny851017.wix.com/home).
